# editorassets/ is populated at release time by goreleaser's before.hooks step:
#   cp -r apps/editor/build/* apps/cli/internal/webassets/editorassets/
#
# Real assets are NEVER committed. Only .gitkeep and this file are tracked.
# The //go:build release guard in embed.go references this directory; without
# real assets present, go build -tags=release will fail (expected in dev/CI).

# Ignore all real build output but keep .gitkeep and this file.
*
!.gitkeep
!.gitignore
